00:29:04.720 --> 00:29:07.920
in the church to borrow a phrase,

707
00:29:07.920 --> 00:29:09.240
but it wasn't over the music.

708
00:29:09.240 --> 00:29:12.440
What were they fighting over in the church in Rome?

709
00:29:12.440 --> 00:29:15.960
It was what kind of food is acceptable to eat in worship?

710
00:29:15.960 --> 00:29:18.640
And also should they observe certain holy days

711
00:29:18.640 --> 00:29:20.280
and not others?

712
00:29:21.200 --> 00:29:23.080
And the answer given as to,

713
00:29:23.080 --> 00:29:25.480
how do they make a call on this?

714
00:29:25.480 --> 00:29:26.320
Well, what to do?

715
00:29:26.320 --> 00:29:28.880
Well, it comes to this.

716
00:29:28.920 --> 00:29:31.320
If you look in chapter 14 and verse six,

717
00:29:31.320 --> 00:29:33.960
it says, what matters most is that they are,

718
00:29:33.960 --> 00:29:38.840
they know that they're motivated by the honor of the Lord.

719
00:29:38.840 --> 00:29:41.520
So like this person chooses to eat this thing,

720
00:29:41.520 --> 00:29:42.360
they think they're free to.

721
00:29:42.360 --> 00:29:44.360
Well, they're doing that to honor the Lord.

722
00:29:44.360 --> 00:29:46.840
This other person refrains from eating this thing over here

723
00:29:46.840 --> 00:29:49.160
and they're doing that in order to honor the Lord.

724
00:29:49.160 --> 00:29:51.080
They say, well, the main thing is that you're both

725
00:29:51.080 --> 00:29:52.800
motivated by the same thing,

726
00:29:52.800 --> 00:29:55.440
which is the glory and esteem of God,

727
00:29:55.440 --> 00:29:58.560
keeping God's glory central.

728
00:29:58.560 --> 00:30:01.880
All right, so desiring the honor of God from the heart

729
00:30:01.880 --> 00:30:05.160
is what's going to unite them together in worship.

730
00:30:05.160 --> 00:30:09.100
They're all besotted together by the glory of the Savior.

731
00:30:10.880 --> 00:30:12.680
Now, don't misunderstand this when it comes to like,

732
00:30:12.680 --> 00:30:14.960
oh, we're really, we're in love with the Savior

733
00:30:14.960 --> 00:30:16.560
and we have these feelings towards Him.

734
00:30:16.560 --> 00:30:19.960
Now, that doesn't mean that worship

