739
00:30:31.600 --> 00:30:33.760
It's responding rightly to God from the heart

740
00:30:33.760 --> 00:30:35.600
even when you're not feeling well.

741
00:30:35.600 --> 00:30:39.200
Like I'm bringing that before the Lord too.

742
00:30:39.200 --> 00:30:41.200
So what does a heart of worship look like?

743
00:30:43.040 --> 00:30:45.280
It's exalting the glory of God

744
00:30:45.280 --> 00:30:47.320
by humbling ourselves before Him.

745
00:30:47.320 --> 00:30:49.960
That's what a heart of worship is.

746
00:30:49.960 --> 00:30:52.280
In the Old Testament, there's two words used for worship.

747
00:30:52.280 --> 00:30:56.640
One is, one means literally to bow yourself down.

